Quote:  My grandfather.. was in charge of two schools, Waikiekie East and Waikiekie West. They were known as 'half time' schools which meant that one group of pupils (averaging 23) would receive tuition from Monday to Wednesday and the second group from Thursday to Saturday. Some keen pupils attended both schools...
